    "### Step 2: Define API Configuration\n",
    "\n",
    "**API Base URL:** https://gamma-api.polymarket.com\n",
    "\n",
    "**Cricket T20 Tag:** tag_id=517 (primary cricket match tag)\n",
    "\n",
    "**Note:** Implementing 1-second delays between requests as courtesy"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# API Configuration\n",
    "API_BASE_URL = \"https://gamma-api.polymarket.com\"\n",
    "CRICKET_TAG_ID = 517  # Primary T20 cricket tag\n",
    "\n",
    "# Request settings\n",
    "REQUEST_DELAY = 1.0  # 1 second delay between requests\n",
    "INITIAL_LIMIT = 20  # Start with 20 markets as proof of concept\n",
    "FULL_DATASET_LIMIT = 1000  # Max markets per API request\n",
    "\n",
    "print(f\"API Base URL: {API_BASE_URL}\")\n",
    "print(f\"Cricket Tag ID: {CRICKET_TAG_ID}\")\n",
    "print(f\"Initial fetch limit: {INITIAL_LIMIT} markets\")"
   ]
  },
