    "### Step 4: Data Validation Functions\n",
    "\n",
    "Validate fetched data for:\n",
    "- Price ranges (0-100¢)\n",
    "- Timestamps (chronological order)\n",
    "- Duplicate detection (by market ID)\n",
    "- Missing or inconsistent data"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
